                TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts83" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts84">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>w haḏāk ʕād az-zilum ši-ysāwūn? ʕād, az-zilum ʕād yirkabūn al-xēl. </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a44"
                TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts87" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts88">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>w yšīlūn al… ar-ridāni, yšīlūn ač-čfūte w ygūm ydaǧǧiǧūn yifitlūn ḥawālē al… al-ᵊhniyye al-biʕīr ygūd wāḥad ygūd al-biʕīr.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
